@POTUS Proud to call for President Trump to award Pat Buchanan with the Presidential Medal of Freedom.

It’s time to honor the man who laid the groundwork for the great political realignment that President Trump led.

Read my full letter here: https://t.co/HVSBKsKf5N

🚨NEW: Today, I’m taking action to secure the Panama Canal by introducing a resolution that calls on Panama to expel Chinese-linked officials from ports on the canal.

@POTUS has made it clear our national security is important, now it’s time to get to work.
https://t.co/R0Xe5Sfmki

We must retain our competitive edge in the skies, especially as China continues to invest in cutting edge technologies. 

My op-ed with @SenatorWicker —&gt; https://t.co/ONp3yEJaDu

@SASCGOP
